desc: Join the Poler Night's and HMD Entertainment team as we head back into the Underground on December 5th 2015 with 3 areas of Booty and Bass from 9p - 4a. Per the usual we bring you to a NEW! exciting Underground location in the heart of Downtown LA. Visually one of the most intruiging locations you will set your eyes upon and the perfect dancefloor to set your soul free. This party will feature some of Los Angeles very best underground DJs and a very special birthday live set from one of the underground scenes favorite sons Esto.   celebrating his 29th Birthday.
